annotationA: Ribosomal protein S28a; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: wing disc development; translation; cytoplasmic translation; rRNA export from nucleus
annotationB: 60S acidic ribosomal protein P0; Ribosomal protein P0 is the functional equivalent of E.coli protein L10; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL10 family
